Name: rf
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-03-27
Author: Giorgi Maghlakelidze <giorgi.snp@pm.me>
Maintainer: Giorgi Maghlakelidze <giorgi.snp@pm.me>
Title: RF and Microwave Network Parameter Utilities
Description: S-parameter network conversions (S<->T, S<->Z, S<->Y, S<->ABCD,
 S<->H, S<->G), de-embedding, cascading, port reordering, renormalization,
 and mixed-mode conversion for differential pairs.
 Provides the utility functions needed to run IEEE P370 de-embedding code
 in Octave without MATLAB's proprietary RF Toolbox.
 This is the first RF/microwave parameter package for GNU Octave.
Categories: RF Microwave Signal-Integrity
Depends: octave (>= 6.0.0)
License: BSD-3-Clause
Url: https://github.com/OpenSNPTools/octave-rf
